<div id="content_table" style="width: 866px;"   >
<br><br>
<h1 class="h1_blue_dark">Sentence Fragments</h1>



  
<table width="866px" bgcolor="#FFFFFF" cellpadding="5" border=0>
<tr><td>
<div>
<h1 class="h1_gray">Introduction</h1>
<br>
In almost every college class you take, you will almost certainly have to do some writing.  
Whether you are emailing your professor, answering questions on an essay exam, or writing a paper, 
your writing in college should represent you well and should be free of grammar errors, including sentence fragments.
<br><br>
This Guided Learning Activity will help you to identify the differences between correct sentences and sentence 
fragments and will teach you how to correct sentence fragments by turning them into correct sentences.<br><br>
</div>
</td></tr>


<tr><td><table width="866px" class="border_green" border=0>
	<tr>
	<td><div>

<strong>By the end of this activity, you should be able to:</strong> <br><br>

	<ul class="c">
<li>Identify the required components of a sentence.</li>
<li>Identify and correct sentence fragments.</li>
	</ul>

</div>
	</td>
	</tr>
</table></td></tr>

<tr><td><div>
<br><br>
<h1 class="h1_gray">Let's get started!</h1><br>

<strong>If at any time you need help, please ask a tutor.</strong><br><br>
</div></td></tr>
<!-- this is the steps table -->
<tr><td>
<table width="866px" border=0>
<tr><td width="80px" valign="top"><h1 class="h1_gray">Step 1: </h1></td>
<td valign="bottom"><div>First you'll need to make sure you have the handouts for this activity. 
If you don't, ask a tutor to help you.<br><br></div></td></tr>

<tr><td width="80px" valign="top"><h1 class="h1_gray">Step 2: </h1></td>
<td><div>Watch the <a href="Fragments.ppt">PowerPoint </a> presentation on Sentence Fragments.  
<br><br></div></td></tr>

<tr><td width="80px" valign="top"><h1 class="h1_gray">Step 3: </h1></td>
<td><div>Once you finish the PowerPoint presentation, complete the "Sentence Fragments" worksheet.<br><br>

STOP and review your worksheet with a tutor.
<br><br></div></td></tr>

<tr><td width="80px" valign="top"><h1 class="h1_gray">Step 4: </h1></td>
<td><div>Complete the quiz and the self-reflection in the handouts.<br><br>
</div></td></tr>

<tr><td width="80px" valign="top"><h1 class="h1_gray">Step 5: </h1></td>
<td><div>Review your work with a tutor.<br><br>
</div></td></tr>

</table>
</td></tr>
         
